    SRV-->>PC: token + ticket
    PC->>SRV: POST /iact8.ph
    SRV-->>PC: signed ActivationRecord

    PC->>iP: SSH tunnel (port 22)
    PC->>iP: Deploy blackhound.dylib
    PC->>iP: Deploy minaeraser12
    PC->>iP: Run Erase_V2 (NAND wipe)
