    iP->>Apple: POST /drmHandshak
    Apple-->>iP: device cert + sig
    Note over iP: Hooked handleActivationInfo<br/>returns Success
    iP-->>PC: iDevice Activated Succesfully

    PC->>iP: iDevice_RemoveProfiles (MDM)
    PC->>iP: BypassMeidSignal (cellular)
    PC-->>U: Display success

